{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-part-intro-template-js","path":"/zh/part6","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<div class=\"intro\">\n<!-- So far, we have placed the application's state and state logic directly inside React components. When applications grow larger, state management should be moved outside React components. In this part, we will introduce the Redux library, which is currently the most popular solution for managing the state of React applications.-->\n<p> 到目前为止，我们已经将应用的状态和状态逻辑直接放在React组件内。当应用规模扩大时，状态管理应该被移到React组件之外。在这一部分，我们将介绍Redux库，它是目前最流行的管理React应用状态的解决方案。</p>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"mainImage":{"publicURL":"/static/a3b7bc3fafcb5b47227616e1343970e5/part-6.svg"},"part":6,"lang":"zh"}}},"pageContext":{"part":6,"lang":"zh"}}}